paramsVOLst.paramValue:
SELECT studyid,
       domain,
       CASE
          WHEN usubjid IS NULL THEN 'nu'
          WHEN usubjid = '' THEN 'nu'
          ELSE REPLACE (usubjid, '-', '')
       END
          AS usubjid,
       miseq,
       CASE
          WHEN migrpid IS NULL THEN 'nu'
          WHEN migrpid = '' THEN 'nu'
          ELSE CAST (migrpid AS STRING)
       END
          AS migrpid,
       CASE
          WHEN mirefid IS NULL THEN 'nu'
          WHEN mirefid = '' THEN 'nu'
          ELSE REPLACE (TRIM (mirefid), '-', '')
       END
          AS mirefid,
       mitestcd,
       mitest,
       CASE
          WHEN miorres IS NULL THEN 'nu'
          WHEN miorres = '' THEN 'nu'
          ELSE TRIM (miorres)
       END
          AS miorres,
       mistresc,
       mirescat,
       michron,
       midistr,
       mistat,
       mireasnd,
       CASE
          WHEN mispec IS NULL THEN 'nu'
          WHEN mispec = '' THEN 'nu'
          ELSE REPLACE (UPPER (mispec), '-', '')
       END
          AS mispec,
       mispccnd,
       mispcufl,
       misev,
       /*DATETIMEFROMPARTS(year(midtc), month(midtc), dayofmonth(midtc), hour(midtc), minute(midtc), second(midtc), 0) as String) */
       getutcdate (midtc) AS midtc,
       midy,
       minomdy,
       minomlbl,
       mineotype,
       mineotypename,
       misize,
       mimod1,
       mimod2,
       mimod3,
       mimod4,
       mimod5,
       mimod6,
       modifiers,
       modifiers2,
       dashed,
       mishorttx,
       mishorttxval,
       mifindingtype,
       phase_name,
       dayofphase,
       CASE
          WHEN SESSION_NUMBER IS NULL THEN 0
          ELSE CAST (session_number AS LONG)
       END
          AS session_number,
       schedule,
       getutcdate (date_time_entered) AS date_time_entered,
       usrref_id,
       user_name,
       comments,
       pmfdat_id,
       pmtfdt_id,
       import_user_name,
       import_dir,
       sedmi_id,
       sedts_id,
       seddm_id,
       trt_fg,
       trt_mod,
       trt_comment,
       action
  FROM mi
/*ORDER BY studyid,  replace(usubjid, '-', ''), phase_name, 
dayofphase, session_number, replace(trim(mirefid), '-', ''), mitestcd,  replace(upper(mispec), '-', ''), MIGRPID*/
